narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: How to run Computational chemistry analyses and determine structural and chemical information using various forms of spectroscopy
You get a good and practical understanding of the theory behind spectroscopy and its application.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I appreciated using and understanding all the different types of spectroscopy and how they related to quantum mechanics. The labs and write ups were also pretty chill.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes! Dont be scared by pchem lab I, this class is a very manageable workload and involves practical applications of pchem!
Yes. I felt like i learned a lot in this class without having to complete a massive workload like 330L.
